TodoMVC Cypress E2E Test Suite

This project contains end-to-end tests for the React-Redux TodoMVC application using Cypress and TypeScript.

## Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+
- npm 9+

## Setup

1. Clone this repository.
2. Install dependencies:

   npm install

## Run tests

- Run all tests headlessly:

	npm test

- Open Cypress interactive runner:

	npm run cy:open

- Run TypeScript checks:

	npm run typecheck

## Project structure

- `cypress/e2e` – test specs
- `cypress/pageobjects` – page object abstractions
- `cypress/elementObjects` – reusable element wrappers
- `cypress/selectors` – page selectors
- `cypress/fixtures` – test data

